**SNOW** — $4.68B FY2026 revenue (+29%), $9.77B RPO (+42%). CEO Ramaswamy's AI pivot (Cortex AI, Snowflake Intelligence) is the right strategy. Stock down 23% YTD to ~$132 (from $300+ highs), now at ~13x P/S. High-risk/high-reward: Microsoft Fabric + Databricks competition, securities lawsuit (Apr 27 deadline), and ongoing GAAP losses are key concerns.
